    "His partnership with Gill ended with the onset of World War II.": [],
    "Richardson moved with the Bartlett School to its temporary quarters at Cambridge, where he rose to full academician in 1944 in the Royal Academy.": [],
    "He became a professor emeritus in 1946.": [],
    "In the post-war years, he embraced preservationist movements.": [],
    "He was president of the Royal Academy of Architects in 1954 and in 1956 he was appointed KCVO.": [
